Property Manager
Ref:AR/260681
Salary: £75000 per annum
Location: Middle East & North Africa, Abu Dhabi
Sector: Real Estate, Property Management
Date: 06 May 2014
Job type: Permanent
Cobalt is currently recruiting a property manager to join a well known and highly regarded developer based in Abu Dhabi
This developer that has been responsible for a number of varying developments across the region. Due to growth, this business is looking to recruit two property managers to sit within the Operations team.
The successful property managers will be well versed in handling and acting on behalf of high profile clients and will understand and be experienced using the Tawtheeq system. Initially, the successful property managers will be tasked with transferring and updating the systems however the role will very much evolve into more of an operations position.
Our client is looking for individuals with a degree and at least 4 years UAE experience. Applicants must be able to work autonomously with little supervision and must have experience dealing with contracts.
Our client is paying up to AED 40,000 per month.
Apply online with your current cv or for further information, please contact Azara Roger at Cobalt Recruitment.
